705948f-a.title: Brooklyn: Nevins Street - State Street
705948f-a.text:
Nevins Street, at the N.W. corner of State Street, showing the
Harriet Judson Y.W.C.A. and Junior League House.
April 24, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
